project: Use the left and right arrow keys (or A and D) to rotate. Use the front and back arrows (or W and S) to move forwards and backwards.
Use the R, G, and B (or 1, 2, and 3) keys to change color to red, green, and blue. Once you have changed color, press space to fire a colored blast.

Ghosts of various colors will appear from the edges of the screen to try and attack you! Whenever you shoot a ghost with a colored blast, it loses the color of the blast you hit it with. Drain the ghost's color completely to destroy it and gain points. Don't let it touch you, or you'll lose a life! Lose all your lives, and it's game over.
